Composed components (separate works, used as external dependencies)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ERO is a thin orchestration layer. It does not vendor or modify the systems it
composes; it consumes their public interfaces. Both are AGPL-3.0-or-later works
by MOBIUS LLC and must be obtained separately:

  * MOBIUS MMV  — answer-entitlement routing runtime
                  https://github.com/mobius-style/mmv
  * MOBIUS RQA  — reflective questioning adapter
                  https://github.com/mobius-style/rqa

Locate them at runtime via the MMV_ROOT / RQA_ROOT environment variables (or as
sibling checkouts). Their copyright, license, and NOTICE terms are preserved in
their own repositories and apply to those works.

